#include <stdio.h>
#include <iostream>
#include <set>
#include <algorithm>

using namespace std;

#define DEBUG 0

int main(){

	//freopen("in","r",stdin);

	set <int> num;
	int N;
	scanf("%d",&N);
	int K;
	scanf("%d",&K);
	num.clear();
	int size[100005]={0};
	for(int tt=0;tt<N;tt++){
		int x;
		scanf("%d",&x);
		if(x!=-1){
			num.insert(x);
			size[x]++;
		}
		else{
			set <int>::iterator it;
			it=num.begin();
			int count=1;
			while(count < K && it != num.end()){
				int nm=*it;
				for(int sz=0; sz < size[nm] ;sz++)
					count+=1;
				if(count > K)
					break;
				++it;
			}
			printf("%d\n",*it);
		}
			
	}
	return 0;

}
